{"tid":2365804,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【肯定係隕石 絕對唔係支那！！！】外媒爆武漢實驗室刪除病毒資料　憂心支那掩蓋真相","createTime":"2021-01-14T04:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T06:46:59.000Z","uid":242537,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"310694ed78ec7be6e64cd479a7d9745f07ae7932","tid":2365804,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:53:12.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎流傳至今，在全球已經造成9030萬例確診案例。而世界衛生組織（WHO）一直希望能進行病毒溯源的工作，但無奈中國不放行，該項工作一直沒有任何進度。而近日有外媒報導，指稱中國政府疑似刪除大量武漢病毒實驗室的資料，憂心中國似乎想要掩蓋真相。<br />\n<br />\n早在新冠肺炎傳播初期，最先的爆發地就是中國湖南省武漢，而又由於武漢當地的病毒實驗室，從事的是蝙蝠冠狀病毒研究，因此武漢一直被外界視為是新冠病毒的發源地，WHO也一直希望能進入該地進行病毒溯源，無奈中國政府一直不肯放行。<br />\n<br />\n而近日《每日郵報》發現，原本在網路上隨時可以查閱的新冠病毒資料，近日遭到刪除，其中包含中國國家自然科學基金委員會（NSFC）發表的300多項研究項目，外界憂心，中國政府此舉疑似要掩蓋新冠肺炎的真相。<br />\n<br />\n這也並非是中國政府首次遭人發現刪除資料，早在2019年12月時，武漢病毒實驗室就開始更改病毒數據庫的資料。當時「野生動物傳播病毒數據庫」被改為「蝙蝠源和鼠源病毒病原數據庫」，一些關鍵字，諸如「新傳染疾病」、「跨物種感染」也遭到刪除。<br />\n<br />\n後來有「蝙蝠女俠」之稱的研究人員石正麗出面解釋，會關閉武漢病毒實驗室的「野生動物傳播病毒數據庫」，是因為當時實驗室的信箱一直遭到駭客攻擊，為了安全起見才關閉實驗數據庫。而在這次的資料刪除事件中，石正麗的研究結果也全數遭到刪除。"},{"pid":"0893a2a6208cb0fa114de64b5f34ca70d9951108","tid":2365804,"uid":242537,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:53:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ctwant.com/article/95867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctwant.com%2Farticle%2F95867&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=c04eaa2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ctwant.com/article/95867</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F677446457296420885%2F690471863515611156%2Fimage0.gif%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1RJvdOz9N-dj3Ul04RsF7eaTV2tn0CflqFrPL7d_VNxZgA6DZUlv3daxM&amp;h=58ada874&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"31d437c40b2d806fa9b33af7916f049599661a69","tid":2365804,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0893a2a6208cb0fa114de64b5f34ca70d9951108","tid":2365804,"uid":242537,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T04:53:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ctwant.com/article/95867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctwant.com%2Farticle%2F95867&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuGWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=c04eaa2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ctwant.com/article/95867</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F677446457296420885%2F690471863515611156%2Fimage0.gif%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1RJvdOz9N-dj3Ul04RsF7eaTV2tn0CflqFrPL7d_VNxZgA6DZUlv3daxM&amp;h=58ada874&amp;s=540\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T05:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732786fc1289fc9bd0414abb93e0f0d43c4ac251","tid":2365804,"uid":28524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T05:26:37.000Z","msg":"年鳩幾，乜record 都化灰啦"},{"pid":"da32b63ea9000b72aa81a8c780adcf006b805aae","tid":2365804,"uid":286017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T05:55:40.000Z","msg":"疑似<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />憂心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />似乎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921561196b8f3db5fc1141816470de0f663f2d3e","tid":2365804,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9791ac45f36c9cd5a59e099364a0b7f3b0f1aa04","tid":2365804,"uid":15830,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:31:36.000Z","msg":"行得正企得正怕咩比人hack比人查仲要刪data<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a653d8ef78fc223fac636a0ed934bf1a27973fb4","tid":2365804,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:46:59.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n<br />\n依家先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=